Gayl Murphy, Founder of Interview Tacticsnbsp;joins Anita Campbell to share how to ldquo;tell it to sell it,rdquo; what the media wants from you, the four questions you will always be asked by gatekeepers, why sound bites are crucial and translating your story into media language.

