<p><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-4664" style="border: #E0E0E0 3px solid;" title="Avoiding A Goat Rodeo" src="http://www.smbtrendwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/goat_rodeo.jpg" alt="Avoiding A Goat Rodeo" width="106" height="160" />Cal Evans, Author of &#8220;<a href="http://avoidingagoatrodeo.com/" target="_blank">Avoiding A Goat Rodeo</a>&#8220; will be joining Anita Campbell and Brent Leary to look at 8 points that people need to consider before contacting their developer. He will dispel the magic of software development and show small business folks how to be involved in the process, keep control of the process, and get the website they want.</p>
<p><strong>Below are the questions we asked Cal</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>(3:39) Cal, can you tell us a bit about yourself and your background and how you came to be involved in web design?</li>
