		<title>How to Protect Your Business When Accepting Payments</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smbtrendwire/rtjZ/~3/Ha3VfLcqCYY/</link>
		<comments>http://www.smbtrendwire.com/2012/01/10/how-to-protect-your-business-when-accepting-payments/#comments</comments>
